          z-index:10;">SAMPLE</span>
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h3 class="panel-title text-center">FullPay Mode</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body text-center">
          <p>Example showing Connect redirect in "FullPay" mode.</>
          <hr width="40%">
          <p>In FullPay mode, your customers are asked for payment, billing and shipping details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#authipayFormModalFullWithCard">Collects Card Details</button>
      <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#authipayFormModalFull">Collects Amount</button>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
